title: Ep222 Unsolved Mysteries
description:
This week, the gals discuss some mysteries that made national news. Topics include a pair of missing grandparents, an abandoned blimp, and an altercation on a bridge, plus an interview with HLN's Susan Hendricks. Google Miss Fisher's 1920s whiskey cocktail, create a Reddit account, and tune in for Unsolved Mysteries.

For a full list of show sponsors, visit www.wineandcrimepodcast.com/support
